14. Face Data Collection and Use (AI Makeup Studio)
AI Makeup Studio uses your device's camera to capture facial photographs for the following purposes:

AI Face Analysis: To generate a personalized beauty and skincare analysis report
AI Makeup Generation: To create virtual makeup looks based on your photo
What face data we collect: Your facial photograph is captured using your device's front-facing camera. On-device facial landmark detection (using Google ML Kit) processes head orientation, smile probability, and eye openness data locally on your device. This on-device data never leaves your phone.

How face data is processed: Your facial photograph is sent securely via encrypted HTTPS connection to Google AI (Gemini API) for face analysis, and to our AI image processing service for makeup generation. These services process your photo in real-time to generate results and return them to the app.

Data retention: Your facial photographs are NOT stored on any server after processing. Photos are transmitted, processed, and immediately discarded by the third-party AI services. No facial photographs or face data are retained, archived, or stored in any database by us or our third-party service providers.

Third-party AI services:

Google AI (Gemini API) — receives your facial photo for beauty analysis. Google's privacy policy applies: https://policies.google.com/privacy
AI Image Processing Service — receives your photo for virtual makeup rendering. Photos are processed in real-time and not stored.
Both third-party services receive only the facial photograph necessary to provide the requested feature. No additional personal information (name, email, location, device identifiers) is sent alongside your photo.

Data sharing: We do not sell, trade, or share your facial photographs or face data with any party for advertising, marketing, analytics, or any purpose other than providing the specific AI feature you requested.

User consent: The app requests your explicit consent before sending any facial photograph to third-party AI services. You may decline, in which case no data is transmitted. Your consent preference is stored locally on your device.

Your rights: Since we do not store your facial photographs or face data on any server, there is no retained data to delete. All processing is transient and real-time.

14.1 AI-Generated Content Disclaimer
All analysis results, beauty recommendations, and skincare advice provided by AI Makeup Studio are AI-generated predictions for entertainment and cosmetic recommendation purposes only. They do not constitute medical diagnosis, dermatological assessment, or health advice. Consult a qualified healthcare professional for any skin health concerns.

